#: ../../language/error_codes/E4108.md:1
msgid "E4108"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4108.md:3
msgid ""
"The loop is expected to yield a value; in current syntax, add a `nobreak`"
" branch."
msgstr "循环需要产生一个值；在当前语法中，请添加 `nobreak` 分支。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4108.md:6
msgid ""
"This error occurs when the compiler infers that a for-loop is expected to"
" yield a non-Unit value based on its context (such as the function's "
"return type), but the loop lacks a branch to provide that value. In "
"current MoonBit syntax, that branch is written as `nobreak`."
msgstr ""
"当编译器根据 for 循环的上下文（例如函数的返回类型）推断出 for 循环应该产生一个非 Unit "
"值，但循环缺少用于提供该值的分支时，就会发生此错误。在当前 MoonBit 语法中，该分支写作 `nobreak`。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4108.md:11
msgid ""
"In MoonBit, when a for-loop is used in a context where a value is "
"expected (for example, when the function returns a non-Unit type), the "
"loop must have an `nobreak` branch that specifies what value to return "
"when the loop completes normally. This is because:"
msgstr ""
"在 MoonBit 中，当 for 循环用于需要值的上下文中（例如，当函数返回非 Unit 类型时），循环必须有一个 `nobreak` "
"分支，用于指定当循环正常完成时应返回的值。这是因为："

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4108.md:16
msgid "The loop body itself cannot yield a value (unlike `loop` expressions)"
msgstr "循环体本身不能产生值（与 `loop` 表达式不同）"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4108.md:17
msgid ""
"Without a `nobreak` branch, there's no way to determine what value should"
" be returned when the loop finishes without breaking"
msgstr "如果没有 `nobreak` 分支，就无法确定当循环正常完成而没有中断时应该返回什么值。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4108.md:20
msgid "This commonly occurs in two situations:"
msgstr "这通常发生在两种情况下："

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4108.md:22
msgid ""
"When the for-loop is the last expression in a function that returns a "
"non-Unit type"
msgstr "当 for 循环是返回非 Unit 类型的函数中的最后一个表达式时"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4108.md:24
msgid ""
"When the for-loop's result is assigned to a variable or used in an "
"expression that expects a non-Unit value"
msgstr "当 for 循环的结果被赋值给一个变量或用于一个需要非 Unit 值的表达式时"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4108.md:27
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4108.md:29
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"pub fn f(x : Int) -> Int {\n"
"  for i = 0, acc = 0; i < x; i = i + 1, acc = acc + i {\n"
"    //^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ Error: The "
"for loop is\n"
"    //                                                      not expected "
"to yield a\n"
"    //                                                      value, please"
" add an\n"
"    //                                                      `else` "
"branch.\n"
"  }\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"pub fn g(x : Int) -> Int {\n"
"  for i in 0..<=x {\n"
"\n"
"  }\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4108.md:33
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4108.md:35
msgid "To fix this error, you can:"
msgstr "要修复此错误，您可以："

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4108.md:37
msgid "add a `nobreak` branch to the for-loop:"
msgstr "向 for 循环添加一个 `nobreak` 分支："

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4108.md:39
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"pub fn f(x : Int) -> Int {\n"
"  for i = 0, acc = 0; i < x; i = i + 1, acc = acc + i {\n"
"\n"
"  } nobreak {\n"
"    acc\n"
"  }\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4108.md:43
msgid ""
"change the function's return type to `Unit` if you don't need to return a"
" value from the loop:"
msgstr "如果您不需要从循环中返回值，请将函数的返回类型更改为 `Unit`："

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4108.md:46
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"pub fn g(x : Int) -> Unit {\n"
"  for i in 0..<=x {\n"
"    ignore(i)\n"
"  }\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

